+11|## D-5d2-2 — builders entry point is over-cap
+12|- **Location**: `packages/fresh/builders/mod.ts` (41.5K, ~1,120 lines).
+13|- **Risk**: single module owns public API contract, types, 
`definePage`/`definePartial`/`defineStatsPartial` signatures, and 
runtime-adjacent interfaces; hard to split without breaking consumers.
+14|- **Impact**: decomposition must preserve `mod.ts` as a thin barrel and move
implementation/implementation types into sub-modules.
