+16|## D-5d2-3 — streaming seam is tightly coupled to builder closure
+17|- **Location**: `packages/fresh/builders/define-page/builder.tsx:362-398`.
+18|- **Risk**: `createStreamingResponse` / `createIncrementalStreamingResponse`
are imported from `server/stream.ts` and invoked inside the generated `GET` 
handler closure, using runtime results (`result.page`, `result.streamLayers`) 
produced by `executePagePipeline`.
+19|- **Impact**: 5d4 (streaming) owns the transport implementation; 5d2 must 
expose a clean page-result type (`{ page, layerData, headers, status, 
streamLayers }`) so 5d4 can wrap without reaching into builder internals.
